Install
-------

.. code-block::

   pip install kleides-mfa


.. code-block::

   MIDDLEWARE = [
       ...
       'django.contrib.auth.middleware.AuthenticationMiddleware',
       'kleides_mfa.middleware.KleidesAuthenticationMiddleware',
       ...
   ]


